text:
Just updating if anyone is interested in contributing to an open source project for hacktoberfest, the <#CBBAW6Z3R|community-browser-extension> has been getting a lot of love, but there are still tons tasks that could be done, and <#CCQSQ2C6L|crankshaft> is still in it’s early days and could use some help too.

So far people have contributed screenshots of the extension, performance improvements, reviewed it’s security, and added language translations to Brazillian Portuguese, French, and Japanese! So cool!
